'''倍里珠'''（{{lang-en|Baily's beads}}，又譯'''貝里珠'''）是[[日食|日食]]（特別是全食與環食）會出現的一種現象。當[[月球|月球]]“掠過”[[太陽|太陽]]時，崎嶇的[[月球邊緣|月球邊緣]]的地形讓陽光在某些地方通過，其他地方卻不行。這個名稱是為了紀念在1836年第一次注意與發現這種現象，並給了正確解釋的[[英國|英國]]天文學家[[弗朗西斯·貝利|弗朗西斯·貝利]]<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1836MNRAS...4...15B
|title=On a remarkable phenomenon that occurs in total and annular eclipses of the sun
|last=Baily
|first=Francis
|work=[[Monthly_Notices_of_the_Royal_Astronomical_Society|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]], Vol. 4, p.15
|bibcode=1836MNRAS...4...15B
|accessdate=2015-10-07
|archive-date=2018-10-27
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181027194107/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1836MNRAS...4...15B
|dead-url=no
}}</ref><ref>{{cite book
|last=Littmann
|first=Mark
|author2=Willcox, Ken|author3= Espenak, Fred
|title=Totality - Eclipses of the Sun
|url=https://archive.org/details/totalityeclipses0000litt
|year= 1999
|publisher=[[牛津大学出版社|Oxford University Press]]
|isbn=0-19-513179-7
|pages=[https://archive.org/details/totalityeclipses0000litt/page/65 65]–66}}</ref><ref>{{cite web
|author=O. Staiger
|title=The Experience of Totality
|url=http://www.mreclipse.com/Totality2/TotalityCh01.html
|accessdate=2015-10-07
